<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Creation du compte administrateur  Club scolaire</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container header-content">
      <a href="/" class="logo">Club scolaire</a>
      <nav class="main-nav">
        <a href="/" class="nav-link">Accueil</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <section class="card" style="max-width:480px;margin:2rem auto;">
        <h1>Créer le compte administrateur</h1>
        <p class="muted small" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
          Cette étape est à faire une seule fois. Choisissez un identifiant et un mot de passe
          pour l'administrateur principal de l'application.
        </p>
        <% if (error) { %>
          <p class="error-inline"><%= error %></p>
        <% } %>
        <form action="/admin/setup" method="post" class="form">
          <div class="form-row">
            <label for="firstName">Prénom</label>
            <input type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <label for="lastName">Nom</label>
            <input type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <label for="ecole">École</label>
            <input type="text" id="ecole" name="ecole" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <label for="filiere">Filière</label>
            <input type="text" id="filiere" name="filiere" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <label for="username">Identifiant</label>
            <input type="text" id="username" name="username" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <label for="password">Mot de passe</label>
            <input type="password" id="password" name="password" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <label for="confirmPassword">Confirmer le mot de passe</label>
            <input type="password" id="confirmPassword" name="confirmPassword" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <button type="submit" class="button button--primary">Créer le compte</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="muted"> <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Club scolaire</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
